{"tid":2348610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直擊元朗鳳姐大廈　尿漬毛巾　被單　口罩佈滿梯間","createTime":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T04:38:00.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"87aa335339253f07685b31d4ee29e39a3ee068f8","tid":2348610,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x_2ARA_g0hQcbnKypO7k7E0cujk=/3840x2160/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CAV5F5EQCBAW3PTGDXCLYYAAPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx_2ARA_g0hQcbnKypO7k7E0cujk%3D%2F3840x2160%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCAV5F5EQCBAW3PTGDXCLYYAAPA.jpg&h=062682fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗色情十街的「三無大廈」被鳳樓進駐，嫖客自出自入。麥超億攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BwOKdQ3HtF5YKmi9uhzkeUc-lnA=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VZ5YO7KIXZHZ7NJOFMZC66UZ6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBwOKdQ3HtF5YKmi9uhzkeUc-lnA%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVZ5YO7KIXZHZ7NJOFMZC66UZ6U.jpg&h=ea2d6bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳳姐在三無大廈梯間排排坐、排排企的場面，日日如是。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dL7cB0EkYf5eoKkOdGzXxfQLyLI=/4608x2592/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y2MLKOTFSJA3ZA4OAZNSEKG7KE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdL7cB0EkYf5eoKkOdGzXxfQLyLI%3D%2F4608x2592%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY2MLKOTFSJA3ZA4OAZNSEKG7KE.jpg&h=5664f0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳳姐大廈內梯間佈滿用過的尿漬毛巾、被單，萬一遇上火警阻礙市民逃生。麥超億攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n三無大廈「冇王管」，雖然民政總署自2011年起推行「大廈管理專業顧問服務計劃」，協助業主成立法團和申請資助等，令其數目由2011年6,600幢減至5,255幢，但個別地區三無大廈數量不跌反升。其中元朗區過去9年竟由262幢增至311幢，《蘋果》走入「色情十街」一帶唐樓，發現部份「鳳姐大廈」即使設有法團，但久久沒有運作，名存實亡，嫖客自出自入，令唐樓重歸三無大廈之列。<br />\n<br />\n大廈大閘24小時中門大開，門鎖被毀，如無掩雞籠，任何人均可自出自入，雖然名義上有法團，但大廈沒有看更、閉路電視或消防設備。在三樓工作的鳳姐稱「擔心唔到咁多」，更反問：「唉！人哋唔關燈唔關火爐都會唔安全，有鐵閘冇鐵閘都冇咩關係？」訪問期間，嫖客上上落落，逐家逐戶「撳鐘仔」，連穿運動裝束的女記者亦被人尾隨。<br />\n<br />\n一家4口住在天台屋近4年的劉女士稱，大閘整好又被破壞，治安成疑，「好多走上嚟又痾屎又痾尿，走上嚟食大麻，好臭呀！乜嘢人都走上嚟，你話係咪散播病毒？」在劉女士身旁的8歲女兒，也按耐不住向記者投訴說﹕「係呀，我哋忍受唔住喇。」另有業主入住6年，發現色情架步有增無減，一樓至六樓也有「一樓一」 ，直言法團形同虛設，只負責聘請阿姐做清潔，搞搞衛生，但其他事一概不理。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210101/74XXN22CZZCWXNBQZT6ASVI3NM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210101%2F74XXN22CZZCWXNBQZT6ASVI3NM%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=2cc3a332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210101%2F74XXN22CZZCWXNBQZT6ASVI3NM%2F&h=90156489\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210101/74XXN22CZZCWXNBQZT6ASVI3NM/</a>"},{"pid":"7d031ae9663cc8b9c1b117fffd4a4102006015d2","tid":2348610,"uid":74012,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:04:08.000Z","msg":"圖中嗰幾條女係咩女嚟??"},{"pid":"37602976f25c15688e8007ca07b7f6220295644c","tid":2348610,"uid":197640,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:08:06.000Z","msg":"呢楝樓同買球拍果座一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e078a6781304abe73c434fe9b586f90af193c14c","tid":2348610,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:10:31.000Z","msg":"女記者好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d8c182681f9febab6e056dbb5cf9191a006513","tid":2348610,"uid":121546,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"咁既